strings.Value: "Soon {name} will become a true {mf|king|queen}. Finally {mf|he|she} will measure to that old goblin king we smacked!"
"Measure to goblin. That's some compliment. Are you happy, {name}?"
"I couldn't even dream of seeing your coronation, {name}. Couldn't even dream of still being here with you..."
"How can one compare pathetic savage to the lawful monarch? Well, I can't expect much from a beast like goblin."
